deck: Kenneth Laramy was running for President of the United States when he killed his wife.
description:
Origin

Kenneth Laramy was a senator running for President of the United States. He killed his wife Courtney, justifying it by telling she fysically abused their daughter Kara. During her funeral he confessed to the murder and got arrested, He riled up the nation during his trial, abusing the words of rapper Reese Greenwood. People plundered and murdered in his name across the nation. Thanks to sympathizers in the justice systems, he was broken out of jail during transport.

Located in a safehouse, he got visited by Reese Greenwood, who got the location of the safehouse from his daughter. Reese discovered that Laramy didn't want to be martyr and begged her to get him out of this. One of his guards heard him and slit Laramy's throat.
name: Kenneth Laramy

deck: Wife of Kenneth Laramy, a senator running for president. She was killed by her husband.
description:
Origin

Courtney Laramy is the wife of Kenneth Laramy and the mother of Kara Laramy. Her husband is running for President of the United States. She was found by her daughter Kara when Courtney was stabbed in the neck. At her funeral, her husband confessed to the nation he had killed her.
name: Courtney Laramy
